}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#3ad28033bd91f6fec060a78ac6680a2a>.
<#3ad28033bd91f6fec060a78ac6680a2a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2cb9200d-57a3-4068-8157-5706fd0c587b>;
