}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#eae7360cbdc0834720be1a55c7201d31>.
<#eae7360cbdc0834720be1a55c7201d31> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/ekk9-4p25>;
