<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#fc54618a25bc02e0961ed9b14af9028d>.
<#fc54618a25bc02e0961ed9b14af9028d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U23200>;
