<https://opendata.umea.se/api/v2/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Umeå kommun", "Leverantörsfakturor"@sv, "Fakturor"@sv, "Accounts payable"@en, "Invoices"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "leverantorsfakturor-2018@http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2120002627";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/SWE>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/43/resource/7a00bd3796ed09a600646432cb321722>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Information om Umeå kommuns inkomna leverantörsfakturor för 2018 finns samlade i denna datamängd. Datat presenteras i tabellform och innehåller konteringsmånad, förvaltning, leverantör, organisationsnummer, konto, kontotext, summa (exkl. moms) och verifikationsnummer. Viss data ��r dolt enligt GDPR. Inga fakturabilder finns presenterade. Informationen går att ladda ner i filformat CSV, JSON och Excel.Vi kan ta fram och skicka fakturakopior med post (ej digitalt) enligt önskemål.Återkom med vilka verifikationsnummer du vill ha kopior på, gärna i excelformat.Skicka in er förfrågan till [leverantorsgruppen@umea.se](mailto:leverantorsgruppen@umea.se)Sida 1-9; Gratis.Sida 10; 50 krSida 11--; 2 kr / sidaPorto tillkommer. Ingen moms debiteras.Vid utdrag avfakturakopior behöver vi era faktureringsuppgifter.Organisationsnummer Namn Kundreferens Adress Postnummer ort "@sv, "Information on Umeå municipality's incoming supplier invoices for 2018 are collected in this data set. The data is presented in tabular form and contains invoice month, departmant, supplier, organisation number, account, account text, amount (exkl. VAT) and verification number. Some data is hidden due to GDPR. No invoice images are presented. The information can be downloaded in file format CSV, JSON and Excel.We can produce and send invoice copies by mail (not e-mail/digital) as desired.Contact us with the verification number that you want copies of, preferably in excel format.Send your request to [leverantorsgruppen@umea.se](mailto:leverantorsgruppen@umea.se)Page 1-9; Free.Page 10; 50 krPage 11--; 2 kr / pagePostage is added. No VAT is charged.For extracting invoice copies, we need your billing information and the address to which the invoice copies are to be sentOrganisation number Name Customer reference Address Zip code City "@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://opendata.umea.se/explore/?refine.dcat.contact_name=Ekonomi%252C+Ume%C3%A5+kommun&refine.dcat.contact_email=leverantorsgruppen%2540umea.se>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018-API>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018-csv>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018-json>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018-jsonl>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018-parquet>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018-rdfxml>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018-jsonld>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018-turtle>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018-n3>, <https://opendata.umea.se/api/explore/v2.1/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2018-xlsx>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-04-09T05:57:56.070000+00:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://opendata.umea.se/explore/dataset/leverantorsfakturor-2018/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2020-04-09T05:57:56.070000+00:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Leverantörsfakturor 2018"@sv, "Accounts payable 2018"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ECON>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>, <http://entryscape.com/terms/ServedByDataService>
}

