_:b0__78879 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Källa: Nationella emissionsdatabasen och SCB\\n"@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N85077> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-06-09"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Utsläpp till luft av växthusgaser, industri, ton CO2e/inv"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/GOVE>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/SOCI>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/REGI>;
